in the same circles.

06:10.971 --> 06:12.637
What is this, an Austen novel?

06:12.740 --> 06:13.939
Gasp.

06:14.041 --> 06:15.474
He reads?

06:15.576 --> 06:16.508
Occasionally.

06:16.610 --> 06:18.443
