06:19.646 --> 06:20.846
Mmm. Who said I was talking
about you?

06:22.750 --> 06:23.749
Oh, that's gonna leave a mark.

06:23.851 --> 06:24.549
Alright, come on.

06:24.651 --> 06:25.450
You are that smart.

06:25.552 --> 06:26.618
You're a nerd.

06:26.720 --> 06:28.720
Nerd is a strong word.

06:28.822 --> 06:30.422
I'm sorry, would you prefer
nerf herder?

06:31.859 --> 06:32.991
Hey, I happen to like
nerf herders.

06:33.093 --> 06:35.727
