a Star Wars fan.

06:35.829 --> 06:37.562
And uh, I may be partial
to nerds, as well.

06:37.664 --> 06:39.898
Especially the humble ones
who have no idea

06:40.000 --> 06:41.366
how pretty they are.

06:41.468 --> 06:42.934
Oh...

06:45.038 --> 06:46.238
how did you know where I live?

06:48.642 --> 06:50.308
