06:54.148 --> 06:55.113
A date with Gus.

06:55.215 --> 06:56.281
Uh, that reminds me,

06:56.383 --> 06:57.215
I should tell him he has plans
on Saturday.

06:59.119 --> 07:00.185
Actually, it wasn't that hard.

07:00.287 --> 07:01.420
People pay attention to you.

07:01.522 --> 07:02.821
Even if you don't realize it.

07:02.923 --> 07:06.958
Well, it's-it's either very
impressive or very creepy.

07:07.060 --> 07:07.826
I'm flattered.

07:07.928 --> 07:09.294
Oh.

07:09.396 --> 07:10.395
Here, come here.

07:10.497 --> 07:12.764
Oh, alright.

07:14.234 --> 07:15.367
Perfect.

07:15.469 --> 07:17.102
Hey, let's get out of this rain.

07:21.074 --> 07:23.008
It went that well, huh?

07:23.110 --> 07:24.342
It was nice.

07:24.445 --> 07:26.711
He um... he invited me and Nikki

07:26.814 --> 07:29.281
