Two dates in one week?

07:31.718 --> 07:32.784
Rob is on the offensive.

07:32.886 --> 07:33.518
I'm impressed.

07:33.620 --> 07:34.820
It's not a date.

07:34.922 --> 07:36.087
It's a party.

07:36.190 --> 07:37.923
