I don't know,

07:50.637 --> 07:52.737
seem like somebody
you need to overthink.

07:54.842 --> 07:56.541
How do you still do it?

07:56.643 --> 07:57.642
What, date?

07:57.744 --> 07:58.777
Yeah.

07:58.879 --> 08:01.913
Well, some people are happy
being alone

08:02.015 --> 08:03.815
and others want a partner.

08:03.917 --> 08:05.283
I'm the second one.

08:05.385 --> 08:06.685
Even after dad?

08:06.787 --> 08:08.119
Especially after your father.

08:09.389 --> 08:10.755
And Rob is nothing
like your dad.

08:10.858 --> 08:12.057
You Googled him?

08:12.159 --> 08:13.525
Obviously.

08:15.095 --> 08:16.495
Oh.

08:16.597 --> 08:18.163
I like seeing you get out
of your comfort zone.

08:18.265 --> 08:19.030
Mmm.

08:19.132 --> 08:20.332
Makes mama very happy.

08:21.602 --> 08:22.300
Happy.

08:22.402 --> 08:23.802
Muah.

08:32.578 --> 08:34.212
Welcome, I'm Alexa.

08:34.313 --> 08:36.313
Bathroom's down there, no
go zone's over to the right,

08:36.416 --> 08:37.916
