over here.

08:38.018 --> 08:39.417
It's Sarah, right?

08:39.520 --> 08:40.184
That's right.

08:40.287 --> 08:41.352
And this is Nikki.

08:41.455 --> 08:42.320
Hey.

08:42.422 --> 08:43.655
Boo!

08:44.024 --> 08:45.423
