09:11.385 --> 09:12.717
Yeah, I like him.

09:12.819 --> 09:16.388
Like... like really like him.

09:16.490 --> 09:17.656
I don't wanna play it cool.

09:17.758 --> 09:20.091
Ok, then don't.

09:20.193 --> 09:21.927
I can't compete with that.

09:23.330 --> 09:27.032
Jacqueline is so beautiful.

09:27.134 --> 09:28.466
Sarah.

09:28.569 --> 09:32.170
The right guy is gonna
like you for you.

09:32.272 --> 09:34.906
