then there's no competition.

09:35.008 --> 09:35.574
Ok.

09:35.676 --> 09:36.341
Ok?

09:36.443 --> 09:37.709
So just go be you.

09:37.811 --> 09:38.510
Uh...

09:38.612 --> 09:39.844
Ok?

09:39.947 --> 09:41.379
Go!

09:43.116 --> 09:44.049
Uh, sort of.

09:44.151 --> 09:45.116
Um... It looks really-

09:45.218 --> 09:46.785
Hey!

09:46.887 --> 09:48.753
Thank you for coming.
I'm so glad you're here.

09:48.855 --> 09:49.387
Oh, well thanks for having me.

09:49.489 --> 09:50.288
Thank you.

09:50.390 --> 09:51.323
You look nice.

09:51.425 --> 09:52.057
Let me introduce you.

09:52.159 --> 09:53.024
Yes.

09:53.126 --> 09:53.992
Hey guys.

09:54.094 --> 09:55.026
Uh, this is Sarah.

09:55.128 --> 09:56.928
Sarah, this is Zach, Alexa...

09:57.030 --> 09:58.763
Happy birthday.

09:58.865 --> 10:00.165
She just met him.

10:00.267 --> 10:01.600
You gotta control your man.

10:01.702 --> 10:03.468
It's his birthday.

10:03.570 --> 10:05.337
He can do whatever he wants.

10:05.439 --> 10:06.638
I got an excuse.

10:12.779 --> 10:16.114
Sometimes I just like to come
out here and clear my head.

10:16.216 --> 10:17.816
You know, when things
get a little much.

10:17.918 --> 10:20.051
Ok.

10:20.153 --> 10:22.420
