10:23.924 --> 10:25.924
Mmm, jury's still out.

10:26.026 --> 10:28.627
Awe, come on.
You trust me.

10:28.729 --> 10:30.228
Close your eyes.

10:36.737 --> 10:38.603
What, did you think
I was gonna drop you?

10:38.705 --> 10:42.107
No, actually.

10:42.209 --> 10:43.508
Good.

10:46.713 --> 10:51.783
Sorry, I guess this isn't the
most traditional first date.

10:51.885 --> 10:54.119
