13:10.157 --> 13:11.389
I can't get past
the first question.

13:11.491 --> 13:12.624
I don't know why.

13:12.726 --> 13:15.527
I don't know how to do
any of... this.

13:17.464 --> 13:18.563
Crap.

13:18.665 --> 13:22.200
Sorry, I-he's... he's freaked
about his essay.

13:22.302 --> 13:23.368
I'll-I'll help you in a sec.

13:23.470 --> 13:24.669
Hang on.

13:24.771 --> 13:25.970
Ok.

13:32.712 --> 13:34.979
You think because English
is easy for you

13:35.081 --> 13:36.347
that it should be easy
for everyone.

13:36.449 --> 13:37.715
Not true.

13:37.818 --> 13:38.917
This is important to me.

13:39.019 --> 13:40.552
Good grades are important
to me.

13:40.654 --> 13:41.953
Yeah.

13:42.055 --> 13:45.890
And if you're gonna be
a distraction then this?

13:45.992 --> 13:47.325
This is a hazard.

13:47.427 --> 13:48.626
