that he wants to get serious.

40:05.771 --> 40:07.570
Just not with me.

40:07.672 --> 40:09.539
No.

40:09.641 --> 40:10.640
Oh, mom, I'm sorry.

40:10.742 --> 40:12.075
Oh, it's ok.

40:12.177 --> 40:14.377
