40:32.130 --> 40:34.330
<i>The shipment was supposed
to be there yesterday.</i>

40:36.435 --> 40:37.767
<i>Ok, you know what?</i>

40:37.869 --> 40:41.604
<i>Um, why don't you give me
20 minutes and I'll handle it.</i>

40:41.706 --> 40:42.705
<i>Yeah, of course.</i>

40:42.808 --> 40:44.374
<i>No problem.</i>

40:50.682 --> 40:52.582
You could knock.

40:52.684 --> 40:54.818
Ok, um, I have to go into work.

40:54.920 --> 40:57.454
Surprise, surprise.

40:57.556 --> 41:00.857
